#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/split.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.split"
msgstr "# triton.language.split"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/split.md:2
msgid "## 1 功能作用说明"
msgstr "## 1 Function Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/split.md:4
msgid "将输入张量沿着最后一个维度分割成两个张量，输出张量的最后一个维度大小为输入张量的一半，其他维度保持不变。"
msgstr "Split the input tensor into two tensors along the last dimension. The last dimension size of the output tensors is half of the input tensor's last dimension, while the other dimensions remain unchanged."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/split.md:6
msgid "**语法：**"
msgstr "**Syntax:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/split.md:8
msgid ""
"- `triton.language.split(input)` - 函数调用形式\n"
"- `input.split()` - 成员函数形式\n"
msgstr ""
"- `triton.language.split(input)` - function call form\n"
"- `input.split()` - member function form\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/split.md:10
msgid "**功能：**"
msgstr "**Function:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/split.md:12
msgid ""
"- 将输入张量沿着最后一个维度分割成两个张量\n"
"- 输出张量的最后一个维度大小为输入张量的一半，最后一个维度的大小必须为2\n"
"- 其他维度保持不变\n"
msgstr ""
"- Split the input tensor into two tensors along the last dimension\n"
"- The last dimension size of the output tensor is half of the input tensor's last dimension size, which must be 2\n"
"- Other dimensions remain unchanged\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/split.md:14
msgid "## 2 参数规格"
msgstr "## 2 Parameter Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/split.md:16
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/split.md:18
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 必需 | 说明 |\n"
"|--------|------|------|------|\n"
"| input | tensor | 是 | 输入张量 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Required | Description |\n"
"|--------|------|------|------|\n"
"| input | tensor | Yes | Input tensor |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/split.md:20
msgid "**返回值：**"
msgstr "**Return value:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/split.md:22
msgid ""
"- **类型：** Tuple[tensor, tensor]\n"
"- **形状：** 两个张量，形状相同，最后一个维度为输入的一半\n"
"- **数据类型：** 与输入张量相同\n"
"- **内存布局：** 分别包含输入张量的奇数和偶数位置元素\n"
msgstr ""
"- **Type:** Tuple[tensor, tensor]  \n"
"- **Shape:** Two tensors with the same shape, where the last dimension is half of the input  \n"
"- **Data type:** Same as the input tensor  \n"
"- **Memory layout:** Contains the elements at odd and even positions of the input tensor, respectively\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/split.md:24
msgid "**约束条件：**"
msgstr "**Constraints:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/split.md:26
msgid ""
"- 输入张量的最后一个维度大小必须为偶数\n"
"- 输出两个张量，形状相同\n"
msgstr ""
"- The size of the last dimension of the input tensor must be even.  \n"
"- Outputs two tensors with the same shape.\n"

