msgid "支持任意维度数、任意形状大小。"
msgstr "Supports any number of dimensions and any shape size."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/split.md:36
msgid "### 2.4 特殊限制说明"
